listing.name: Exclusively located Penthouse

user.about:
I live in Amsterdam and love living here!  
I am so lucky to live in the same building with my brother. Will you join us for some time ? :)
After 10 years the building I live in needs some restoration
the way an old building (build around 1880) deserves.
By staying in my house you help me with funding this restoration.
Thank you so much and see you soon!

Ciao
Frans
